SIMPLE: apron_string
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Apron string
<hw>A"pron string`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <def>The string of an
apron.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><mcol><col><b>To be tied to a wife's apron strings</b></col>
<it>or</it> <col><b>To be tied to a mother's apron
strings</b></col></mcol>, <cd>to be unduly controlled by a wife or
mother.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He was so made that he could not submit <qex>to be tied to the
apron strings</qex> even of the best of wives.</q>
<rj><qau>Macaulay.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Apropos</ent>⟦br⟧
